    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "was a monthly publication which carried information and intelligence",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "research by [REDACTED] on flying objects. According to [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the [REDACTED] had a limited circulation.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "In connection with Dr. [REDACTED] letter, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "stated that prior to the receipt of the letter he received a long",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "distance telephone call from Dr. [REDACTED] on March 12, 1957. This",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "call was received by him in the early morning prior to his departure",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "for work. He related that Dr. [REDACTED] was a subscriber to the [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "and that during the phone conversation she made reference to some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
